, 124.6042, 125.794, 129.5534, 128.6134, 129.6451, 129.0997, 129.33, 128.6269, 127.1473, 123.4641, 126.0485, 128.1961, 128.9849, 129.2321, 128.1123, 127.9072, 129.2019, 129.2365, 130.6459, 131.4249, 131.1858, 129.9572, 131.2637, 132.3986, 130.9454, 130.7777, 131.4882, 131.0492, 132.8479, 133.0566, 133.6072, 133.4175, 133.2709, 133.5454, 134.1983, 134.6224, 135.9407, 136.5297, 136.392, 135.4015, 135.2689, 133.931, 134.3537, 136.1791, 135.6534, 134.6607, 134.2732, 134.2044, 134.7269, 134.0644, 133.809, 134.0748, 134.8671, 135.5038, 134.36, 135.104, 135.0536, 135.3728, 135.675, 136.5834, 136.9553, 135.5674, 136.2994, 136.8384, 135.2964, 133.7413, 132.086, 132.712, 133.9395, 134.176, 134.4428, 134.1467, 133.8457, 133.5825, 136.1026, 135.2242, 135.2603, 135.5803, 137.3827, 136.6813, 137.6432, 138.7706, 137.4181, 137.2106, 138.0166, 137.3597, 137.1827, 137.4244, 138.2812, 138.3899, 137.8832, 138.2435, 138.4244, 138.4355, 138.9811, 138.3965, 138.6845, 138.5251, 138.094, 137.9721, 137.5231, 138.2198, 138.7436, 139.1171, 139.7106, 140.1576, 140.0993, 139.2321, 138.4895, 137.802, 137.9781, 137.6051, 138.6044, 137.6962, 138.3972, 137.033, 136.6609, 138.9447, 137.9848, 139.4067, 140.1273, 140.4739, 140.7223, 141.0913, 142.3471, 143.5172, 142.9607, 144.4576, 143.2796, 143.8117, 143.9693, 144.6131, 145.232, 143.897, 146.0731, 146.8226, 146.9461, 148.3434, 150.0187, 151.861, 151.1084, 150.102, 152.1525, 152.2248, 152.3497, 152.4341, 151.6797, 153.0685, 153.9709, 153.923, 155.129, 156.9303, 157.5357, 157.878, 155.9285, 156.9065, 156.3528, 156.6493, 156.2973, 156.4904, 157.1347, 160.4786, 159.1409, 159.6576, 160.4577, 160.1098, 159.5708, 160.6393, 156.827, 156.1584, 156.1635, 155.4236, 156.0382, 156.2592, 153.8445, 154.6165, 155.5382, 156.2281, 156.3751, 155.6029, 154.4257, 153.8725, 153.6858, 153.6052, 153.7907, 152.359, 152.8695, 150.1089, 145.8858, 145.8824, 144.427, 144.6883, 147.5508, 146.5748, 148.1738, 150.0997, 150.0494, 148.3296, 146.8894, 146.7026, 146.4148, 146.4406, 146.1209, 144.286, 145.3862, 144.8616, 145.1873, 146.334, 147.3556, 148.0392, 149.5386, 149.2248, 149.0217, 150.1068, 150.189, 150.3953, 151.5374, 152.2439, 152.1408, 152.8105, 151.9079, 150.5814, 150.9063, 151.5519, 151.382, 150.9703, 151.1406, 148.9347, 149.7174, 149.2707, 150.1432, 149.0622, 150.2801, 151.2644, 150.5043, 151.03, 152.4933, 153.737, 155.003, 156.8797, 155.829, 154.6189, 154.2746, 155.2879, 154.4035, 154.7581, 154.7156, 155.0729, 155.2999, 156.0007, 156.4578, 155.9984, 156.7445, 155.3158, 156.5322, 157.245, 157.6851, 157.4641, 158.13, 157.0582, 156.7362, 156.668, 157.6042, 157.3112, 156.0658, 157.3479, 157.7592, 158.5183, 157.8149, 158.9857, 158.5496, 158.054, 157.2638, 157.6093, 157.9719, 157.7309, 157.1549, 156.5437, 156.8593, 156.485, 158.0847, 157.8417, 158.2181, 159.1115, 158.7666, 159.043, 157.8938, 157.3674, 157.4516, 156.2339, 156.8986, 158.1554, 157.011, 156.9214, 158.1513, 157.1871, 157.5659, 156.0667, 155.6391, 156.487, 154.4683, 152.7591, 153.0149, 153.4197, 152.5599, 153.0503, 152.1436, 151.6607, 152.2091, 152.6128, 152.6577, 152.537, 152.3363, 151.259, 151.9792, 152.7103, 151.6421, 151.1247, 151.4525, 151.0044, 151.4503, 151.2621, 151.9632, 152.0931, 152.1275, 152.2494, 154.2194, 153.4791, 154.784, 154.5455, 156.0067, 155.9637, 158.3393, 158.9774, 155.1796, 157.1199, 155.7359, 154.0604, 152.8193, 158.1997, 154.1432, 154.7588, 152.9098, 150.9652, 150.6011, 146.8857, 144.8944, 143.9784, 143.5945, 143.372], "summary_html": "<h1>GTJA CTA 多因子回暖系列十四 -- 截面多因子组合</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>报告梳理了国泰君安期货 CTA 商品因子体系的六大类因子 (时序动量、截面动量、截面库存、截面仓单、期限结构、截面偏度), 展示了各因子在 2023 年 6-9 月的表现并与 CTA 私募产品净值做对比。本复现提取报告定义的全部因子类别, 在全品种商品期货上构建截面多因子模型。</p>\n<p>最终最优变体为三因子组合: <strong>截面偏度 (skew_120) + 期限结构 (ry_s40) + 仓单变化 (rcpt_chg_80)</strong>, 权重 40/40/20, 每 20 日换仓。截面偏度因子利用 120 日收益率偏度的截面排名, 做空高偏度品种 (上涨不对称、均值回归预期), 做多低偏度品种; 期限结构因子利用 40 日平滑展期收益率的截面排名, 做多 contango 品种 (正向展期); 仓单因子利用 80 日仓单变化率排名, 做空仓单增加的品种 (供给端压力)。三因子组合后信号更平滑、更稳健。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>7.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>7.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-16.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2644</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.15</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-1.08</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.36 / 1.0</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.68</td><td>1.61</td><td>1.47</td><td>1.19</td><td>0.99</td><td>1.73</td><td>1.9</td><td>0.91</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.85</span></td><td>0.35</td><td>1.48</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.85</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 120 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 120 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2646</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>35.8</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>偏度因子:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{skew}_{i,t} = \\text{Skewness}\\left(\\ln\\frac{P_{i,\\tau}}{P_{i,\\tau-1}}\\right)_{\\tau \\in [t-120, t]}</div>\n<p><strong>期限结构因子:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ry\\_s40}_{i,t} = \\frac{1}{40} \\sum_{\\tau=t-39}^{t} \\text{ry}_{i,\\tau}</div>\n<p><strong>仓单变化因子:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rcpt\\_chg80}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{receipt}_{i,t}}{\\text{receipt}_{i,t-80}} - 1</div>\n<p><strong>组合信号:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = -0.4 \\cdot R(\\text{skew}_{i,t}) + 0.4 \\cdot R(\\text{ry\\_s40}_{i,t}) - 0.2 \\cdot R(\\text{rcpt\\_chg80}_{i,t})</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">R(\\cdot)</span> 为截面百分位排名映射到 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, 1]</span>。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>6 类因子全部实现, cs_skew_120 Sharpe 0.83 最优, term_struct_s40 紧随 (0.82)</td><td>实现所有因子类别 (tsmom/csmom/inventory/receipt/term_struct/skewness), 以截面排名+连续信号方式输出</td><td>偏度和期限结构因子表现突出, 动量和库存因子较弱</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>偏度+期限结构两因子是核心; turnover 0.56 偏高</td><td>1) 偏度窗口网格 [40-180]; 2) skew+ts 组合权重网格; 3) 加入 3 因子 (skew+ts+receipt)</td><td>Sharpe 提升到 1.09 (sk120_ts40 combo), turnover 降至 0.31, 3 因子组合也达 1.07</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>combo 信号稳健, 3 因子方向正确</td><td>1) 精细化 skew [100-150] x ts [30-50] 网格; 2) 3 因子组合网格 (receipt lookback [40-80]); 3) vol-target + IC gate</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.33</strong> (str_120_40_80), 回撤仅 -25.6%, 半样本检验 1.82/1.11 稳定</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R1 发现偏度因子出人意料地强 (Sharpe 0.83), 超过了报告重点强调的动量因子。R2 将偏度与期限结构组合后突破 1.0。R3 加入仓单因子 (80 日变化率) 形成三因子组合, 进一步提升至 1.33 并大幅压缩回撤。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部商品期货 (~56 个活跃品种), 依赖 ry/receipt 字段 (非空率 ~37%/23%)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20 天换仓</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 与因子库 bohai carry 因子相关性 0.52 (边界冗余); 2023-2024 年表现较弱 (偏度信号在低波动环境效果打折)</li>\n<li><strong>NAV 终值 9.89x</strong>: 实际敞口较大 (年化波动率 0.78), 如需控制风险可使用 vol-target 版本</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>SKEW_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>120</code></td><td>rolling skewness lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>RY_SMOOTH</code></td><td><code>40</code></td><td>roll-yield smoothing window</td></tr><tr><td><code>RCPT_LB</code></td><td><code>80</code></td><td>receipt change-rate lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>rebalance hold period</td></tr><tr><td><code>W_SKEW</code></td><td><code>0.4</code></td><td>skewness weight (negated in combo)</td></tr><tr><td><code>W_TS</code></td><td><code>0.4</code></td><td>term-structure weight</td></tr><tr><td><code>W_RCPT</code></td><td><code>0.2</code></td><td>receipt weight (negated in combo)</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 1.14s</li>\n</ul>"}